        <h1><c>Here are some tips that can be of assist to complete your next task.</c></h1>
        <!--Here I list tips that will help the user gain more information as to completing their tasks in time smoothly-->
            <h2>-Prioritize tasks by splitting the task up into small objectives.</h2>

            <h2>-Work on the task during the most productive time and try to avoid distractions.
            </h2>
            <h2>-Make sure you take a break to avoid working for long continuous hours.</h2>
            <h2>-After you complete a part of the task, re-prioritize the task.</h2>
            <h2>-Ensure that you do not work for long hours and that you include some fun activies to feel refreshed.</h2>
            <h2>-Get an ample amount of nights sleep to recover and tackle the objective the next day.</h2>
